column5: Anybody wanna go for an evening fish tonight? Thinking of leaving town around 230, maybe earlier. I'll be driving out in my truck....blair, joey, luc...anyone else?  Winds are at 15kph, so they'll be nice walleye chop out there
Haha dang it. I need more notice or I would have gone. Good luck tonight.
4 hour drive, it's 1030, meet at 2:30.....perfect!! haha
Way too busy man..LSPP bound this weekend
all you need are a couple lunches, 100 feet of line, some hooks and a pack of worms. What's the big deal?
Looks like it'll be a solo trip. 10 pounder for sure tonight.
